ly typing in a different birthday. That\u2019s it. That\u2019s the system.\u201d This implies self-reported dates won\u2019t be sufficient.</p>\n<p>Experts and critics expect the law to mandate stronger verification, such as uploading a driver\u2019s license, passport, or using a digital ID. Once verified, your OS would issue a trusted signal (e.g., \u201cverified over 18\u201d) to apps and services\u2014without revealing your full identity, but still creating a traceable identity anchor tied to your device.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 7, "score_up": 36, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZR1s59r", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 30, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8562417, "raw_content": "", "author": "rdvs34283", "created": 1776348004419, "profile_picture": "p9HQtdiLq2uP", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Valiazaner", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.thegatewaypundit.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZR1s59r.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.thegatewaypundit.com/2026/04/fafo-american-youtuber-sent-prison-south-korea-disrespecting/", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "American YouTuber Sent to Prison in South Korea for Lap Dance on Public Statue Honoring WWII Sex Slaves.", "last_comment_created": 1776355249409, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, 